feature/passwd-expire
---------------------

It provides a mechanism by template feature/passwd-expire to force users to
update their passwords when next time serial or graphical login. For graphical
login, it only support display manager 'lxdm' for now.

Introduce 2 variables:
* FORCE_PASSWD_EXPIRE:
  The flag whether this feature is enabled, and it should not be disabled.

* FORCE_EXPIRED_USERS:
  It works with EXTRA_USERS_PARAMS which is from extrausers.bbclass. Users set
  in FORCE_EXPIRED_USERS will be promted to update the passwords when next time
  serial or graphical login.


#@TYPE: Wrtemplate
#@NAME: passwd-expire
#@DESCRIPTION: Force users to update passwords when next time serial or graphical login
